No AI Training / No Commercial Model Use (Additional Restriction)

In addition to the terms above, the following restriction applies:

1. Prohibited Uses. You MAY NOT use the Software, or any portion of it, to train, fine-tune, evaluate, or otherwise create or improve a machine learning model, foundation model, or other automated system (collectively, "Models"), whether for research, commercial, or other purposes. This includes, without limitation:
   a. Including the Software in any dataset used to train or fine-tune a Model;
   b. Using Model outputs generated from a Model trained (directly or indirectly) on the Software to provide a commercial product or service;
   c. Repackaging, redistributing, sublicensing, or otherwise making available Models trained on the Software for commercial use.

2. Commercial Licensing. If you wish to use the Software for training Models or to offer a service that uses Models trained on the Software, you must obtain a separate commercial license from Reqsery. See COMMERCIAL-LICENSE-CONTACT.md for contact details and licensing inquiries.

3. Attribution and Notice. Any permitted use of the Software must include the copyright notice above and reference to this license.

4. Enforcement. This restriction is intended to be legally enforceable. If you are unsure whether your use is permitted, contact the copyright holder for written permission prior to such use.

